cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper proposes a scalable image compression scheme for facial images, which is a common topic in computer vision research. 
2. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The proposed scheme involves compressing and reconstructing multimedia data, specifically facial images. 
3. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses rate-accuracy and rate-distortion performance, which are concepts related to information theory. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The base layer of the proposed scheme is designed using deep learning features, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses the performance of the proposed scheme in comparison to conventional image compression schemes, which is a topic related to multimedia research.
